  "issue_title": "[bug] tools/dispatch: home_status accepts missing/empty entity with silent default (same gap as fixed #330 for home_control)",
  "issue_body": "### Summary\n\n`ToolDef` for `home_status` marks `entity` as required, but `exec_home_status` substitutes `\"\"` for missing/invalid values and proceeds to Home Assistant lookup. #330 fixed this enforcement gap for `home_control`; `home_status` still bypasses the typed-tool schema at execution time.\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\n1. On an x86_64 Linux dev host:\n   ```bash\n   cd genie-claw\n   ```\n2. Confirm schema vs execution mismatch:\n   ```bash\n   sed -n '365,373p' crates/genie-core/src/tools/dispatch.rs   # required entity\n   sed -n '879,887p' crates/genie-core/src/tools/dispatch.rs   # unwrap_or(\"\")\n   ```\n   **Pass (bug present):**\n   ```rust\n   \"required\": [\"entity\"]\n   // ...\n   let entity_name = args.get(\"entity\").and_then(|v| v.as_str()).unwrap_or(\"\");\n   ```\n3. Add a failing integration test (pattern from closed #330 / `tool_gate_integration_test.rs`):\n   ```rust\n   let result = dispatcher.execute_with_context(\n       &ToolCall { name: \"home_status\".into(), arguments: serde_json::json!({}) },\n       ToolExecutionContext { request_origin: RequestOrigin::Dashboard, ..Default::default() },\n   ).await;\n   assert!(!result.success); // FAILS on main \u2014 proceeds with entity \"\"\n   ```\n4. Repeat with `{\"entity\":\"\"}` and non-string `\"entity\": 123`.\n\n### Expected behavior\n\n- Missing, empty, or wrong-type `entity` \u2192 `success: false`, clear schema error, tool audit entry, **no** HA / `FakeHomeProvider` side effect.\n- Valid `home_status` calls unchanged (existing quick-router and dispatch tests still pass).\n\n### Actual behavior\n\n- `{}` or `{\"entity\":\"\"}` \u2192 empty entity string passed to `home::status`.\n- Schema in `tool_defs()` is not enforced at the execution boundary.\n- BFCL/local-LLM strict argument scoring can expect valid entities while runtime silently accepts invalid calls.\n\n### Hardware\n\nNon-Jetson (x86_64 dev / cross-build host)\n\n### JetPack / L4T version\n\n_No response_\n\n### GenieClaw version / commit\n\nv1.0.0-alpha.10 / `main`\n\n### Relevant logs\n\n```shell\n\n```\n\n### Additional context\n\n**Suggested files:** `crates/genie-core/src/tools/dispatch.rs`, `crates/genie-core/tests/tool_gate_integration_test.rs`.",
